## Alert Details
 
Further investigation of the alert showed:
 
* Source IP: 10.0.0.5
* Destination IP: 10.0.0.4
* Username Targeted: administrator
* Total Events: 20
* Detection Rule: SMB Brute Force Detection Rule
The alert metadata confirmed that the event volume exceeded the configured threshold and was consistent with automated credential guessing activity, and mapped the activity to MITRE ATT&CK Credential Access (T1110, T1110.001).
 
